::Zeus/Annihilator/Killer::

Zeus walks out of the CR room on Set's and Shuko's ship. He flexes his arm, 
making sure it was repaired. Walking out of the base, he nearly trips over 
Annihilator, who was laying face first on the floor with Killer bahind him.

He grunts and picks up the two predacons. Slightly disgusted, he drags them 
off towards the CR chambers.
